description:
Meeting people and gaining insights from the experts will take your skills to the next level! This is your chance to experience in-person learning on November 12-15 in Salt Lake City at the KubeCon + CloudNativeCon 2024! See you there!

Learn more: https://events.linuxfoundation.org/kubecon-cloudnativecon-north-america/
